# RELEASE

## Version: 0.0.2
- Modularized DataWedge intent handling (DataWedgeHelper)
- Improved user feedback (Toasts, dialogs)
- Progress dialog for scanning operations
- Documentation and onboarding improvements
- Date: March 29, 2026

## Version: 0.0.1
- Consolidated DataWedge Notification API for real-time hardware status monitoring.
- Implemented dual-status UI for Barcode Scanner and RFID Sled.
- Added explicit SET_CONFIG result handling to detect missing hardware.
- Modernized status bar UI with color-coded indicators.
- Fixed duplicate class and package name conflicts.
- Date: April 2, 2026
